data.description: **$3000 REALTOR BONUS** Beautiful One-Story Home with Underground Pool and Detached Garage on Half-Acre Lot     Welcome to your dream home in the charming South East side of San Antonio! This spacious and meticulously maintained one-story residence offers the perfect blend of comfort, style, and outdoor living. With four bedrooms, two bathrooms, and a fantastic underground pool, this property is an oasis of relaxation and entertainment.     Bedrooms: 4   Bathrooms: 2   Pool: Underground   Garage: Detached   Lot Size: Half an Acre    As you approach the home, you'll be captivated by the lush landscaping and the expansive front yard, offering plenty of space for outdoor activities or gardening enthusiasts. The detached garage provides ample room for your vehicles, storage, or a workshop for your hobbies.    Inside, the home boasts an open and inviting floor plan. The spacious living room features large windows, allowing natural light to flood the space, creating a warm and welcoming atmosphere. The kitchen is a chef's delight with modern appliances, plenty of counter space, and a convenient breakfast bar.    The four bedrooms offer versatility and space for your family's needs. The master suite is a tranquil retreat with an en-suite bathroom, complete with a luxurious soaking tub and separate shower.    One of the property's highlights is the underground pool, offering you the ultimate escape on hot Texas days. Imagine lounging by the poolside, hosting barbecues, and creating lasting memories with family and friends.    Located in the sought-after South East side of San Antonio, this home provides easy access to schools, shopping, dining, and entertainment. It's the perfect balance of serene suburban living while still being close to all the conveniences of the city.    Don't miss the opportunity to make this beautiful one-story home yours. Schedule a showing today and start living the Texas dream!    For more information or to schedule a viewing, please contact agent. Act fast; this property won't stay on the market for long!
